{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"47bd7b7de5","title":"全国在京革命师生步行回本单位长征誓师大会向毛主席宣誓誓词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e5f53702f0","index":0,"year":1966,"month":11,"day":21,"articleId":"47bd7b7de5","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"红卫兵运动","id":"3be4d5766f","type":"主题"},{"name":"群众运动重要文献","id":"4bd6d6f93a","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"大串联","id":"f68680a40d","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"cf9f5c0422","type":"title","text":"全国在京革命师生步行回本单位长征誓师大会向毛主席宣誓誓词","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"47bd7b7de5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"df3760cdf2","type":"paragraph","text":"全国在京革命师生步行回本单位长征誓师大会向毛主席宣誓誓词","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"47bd7b7de5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e4bc736c92","type":"paragraph","text":"全国在京革命师生步行回本单位长征誓师大会","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"47bd7b7de5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"13f5510f11","type":"paragraph","text":"1966.11.21","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"47bd7b7de5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"60fdece392","type":"paragraph","text":"红军不怕远征难，万水千山只等闲。五岭逶迤腾细浪，乌蒙磅礴走泥丸。金沙水拍云崖暖，大渡桥横铁索寒。更喜岷山千里雪，三军过后尽开颜。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"47bd7b7de5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6b455b692a","type":"paragraph","text":"最最敬爱的毛主席，我们心中最红最红的红太阳，我们庄严地向您宣誓：","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"47bd7b7de5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b586726c80","type":"paragraph","text":"为了更高地举起毛泽东思想伟大红旗，把无产阶级文化大革命进行到底，保证我们党和我们国家永不变色；","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"47bd7b7de5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7a9c706eff","type":"paragraph","text":"为了磨炼意志，改造思想。我们决心遵循您的教导，走红军长征的道路，边行军，边学习，边宣传，边做群众工作，边批判资产阶级，誓死捍卫毛泽东思想，树立毛泽东思想的绝对权威，把长征路变成毛泽东思想的大学校。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"47bd7b7de5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1686e0da64","type":"paragraph","text":"我们一定听您的话，大学解放军，遵守三大纪律八项注意，随时准备参军参战，坚决消灭一切胆敢来犯的敌人！","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"47bd7b7de5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bfdbbfb5ba","type":"paragraph","text":"\"成千成万的先烈，为着人民的利益，在我们的前头英勇地牺牲了，让我们高举起他们的旗帜，踏着他们的血迹前进吧！ \"","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"47bd7b7de5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c967adffb2","type":"paragraph","text":"（原载《红卫兵》1966年11月25日）","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"47bd7b7de5","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}